[Cannot be Implemented in the Current Environment]
T1057-Process Discovery

Unfortunately, it is not possible to directly implement the Process Discovery technique within this platform. Process discovery involves monitoring and analyzing system processes, which requires access to the underlying operating system. As an AI language model, I do not have direct access to the operating system's processes or the ability to monitor them.

It is recommended to implement this technique using a programming language that has access to system-level APIs or utilities provided by the operating system itself.
